title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
05-07-11-20-31
(five, seven, eleven, twenty, thirty-one)
